channel.title: Recruiting Professional Developers For 317 loading 602 DeadMan Rsps
channel.description:
Hello my name is nivri, i am not new to the game of RSPS's. I have owned multiple succesful, and failed projects. I met alot of interesting people along the path. I have had multiple names, and i may know alot of you. I decided to come back into the game, because i never truly accomplished what i wanted when i was younger. And that was a thriving RSPS. I now have the resources & funding, to make this happen. If you are looking to join, my team. Then you must meet at least one of the following criteria's:
[ol][li]17 of age+[/li] [li]High Graphics skills[/li] [li]Website designer[/li] [li]High Pi knowledge base[/li] [li]Have owned multiple servers before[/li][/ol]
My requirements are high, because i am shooting high. If you have a base, you would like to start on then pm me and we can talk about it.
Now some of you guy's are asking yourself's....What does he have to offer?
About me... I have owned multiple servers. (players ranged from, 20 to 60) I have managed forums and websites. (I own currently a forum community, with paid sponsors and advertisements. Have personal mybb designers creating a 200$ theme on it as we speak.) I know and understand above average java coding. (I know some client sidded and server sided, basic fundamentals. I have a Vps and domain ready to be activated. (I own multiple vps, because of my connections.) I can promote the rsps. (I am not afraid, of spending money. I easily spent nearly 200$ on just promos for my forum.) I have proper funding. (I have a career.)
[b]This project well not fail, because i well not fail.[/b] Lets make this happen.
To join this project post below, with the following format.
[ul][li]Skype[/li] [li]Experince[/li][/ul]
